description:
Hello Bristol Gophers 👋!

We're continuing with the workshops!

New Lesson: Secrets

Lessons: https://github.com/bristolgolang

On top of the lessons we encourage you to bring your own problems and we can work through them together.

Plan:

* 18:00 - Arrive anytime after
* 18:15 - Intro and pizza
* 18.20 - Get Started
* 20:00 - Finish up

🍺 Optionally, we will be heading to a pub for a little afterwards.

📣 We are looking for help with organising! If you or anyone you know would like to help, give us a shout!

❤️ Sponsors

* Tumelo (venue)
* Formula Recruitment (food/drinks)

📍 - Runway East
